Let Gtk handle tooltips

Add a TOOLTIP_COLUMN to the model,
store the text there (when appropriate),
and let the tree display tooltips automatically.

usbview 3.0 release

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

usbview.spdx: add spdx file

Make the SBOM tools happy.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

Add copyright and license info to many files that were missing it.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

INSTALL: remove file

It contained boilerplate autotools text, no need to have it in here.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

Add license to AUTHORS and Changelog file

Trying to make the project 'spdx lint' clean.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

TODO: delete file

We don't need anything else to do here in this project except move the
whole logic into usbutils.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

add proper license and license info for the CCAN files

This brings in the CC0 and MIT licenses into the LICENSES/ directory to
properly attribute the ccan provided files.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

usbtree.c: update copyright year

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

sysfs.c: rename comment and update copyright date

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

usbparse: remove old debugfs/usbfs parsing logic entirely

The parsing of the usb devices is all done through sysfs now, so remove
the old usbparse.h and .c files as they are no longer needed.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

sysfs.h: remove typedef for DeviceEndpoint

Just use the structure name instead.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

sysfs.h: remove typedef for DeviceInterface

Use the structure name instead.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

sysfs.h: remove DeviceConfig typedef

Just use the structure name instead.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

sysfs.h: remove typedef for DeviceBandwidth

Just use the struct name instead.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

sysfs.h: remove typedef for Device

Use the struct name instead.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

.h: remove extern from function declarations.

It's not needed.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

sysfs.h: fix comment and filename

Also update the copyright and remove some whitespace

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

sysfs.h: remove unused #defines

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

usbtree: remove unused file handling logic

No need for filehandling logic anymore, there is no file to parse!

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>

usbview_logo: remove copyright year from graphic

Too much of a pain to keep updating the graphic when the
year changes.

Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>
Makefile.am: add ccan include files
